# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../import_export.rst:21
msgid "Import & Export"
msgstr "Impor & Ekspor"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../import_export.rst:23
msgid ""
"Video editing projects (including tracks, clips, and keyframes) can be "
"**imported** and **exported** from OpenShot Video Editor in widely supported "
"formats (**EDL**: Edit Decision Lists, and **XML**: Final Cut Pro format). "
"For example, if you start editing a video in a different program (Adobe "
"Premier, Final Cut Pro, etc...), but later need to move all your edits to "
"OpenShot (or vice versa)."
msgstr ""
"Proyek pengeditan video (termasuk trek, klip, dan keyframe) dapat "
"**diimpor** dan **dieksport** dari OpenShot Video Editor dalam format yang "
"banyak didukung (**EDL**: Edit Decision Lists, dan **XML**: format Final Cut "
"Pro). Misalnya, jika Anda mulai mengedit video di program lain (Adobe "
"Premiere, Final Cut Pro, dll...), tetapi kemudian perlu memindahkan semua "
"editan Anda ke OpenShot (atau sebaliknya)."

